parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the transmission can cause the vehicle to hesitate, jerk, or stall, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: the transmission slips or feels broken
the vehicle takes off in 4th gear instead of 1st gear
and clunks when launching from a stop or rolling stop.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the brakes can cause the vehicle to lose control, leading to accidents or injuries.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the engine can cause the vehicle to stall or lose power, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the drivetrain can cause the vehicle to vibrate excessively, leading to accidents or loss of control.
